replies.body:
Hi I want to ask you something that happens when you find someone interested in Freljord.

You know the new Lissandra lore has been released.
At the end of Lore;
Lissandra watches them carefully, seeking any opportunity to pit them against one another, all the while redoubling her own efforts to lock away the terrible secrets she has buried deep under her citadel.

And she must hurry, for the ice is beginning to melt.

These reminders reminded me of the chain champion on the championship road map that was broadcast to me. Is that possible ? Because the Rioters told me they would give more information about Lissandra and watchers. Can they do this by the new champion? I do not speak English very well,I hope you understand me. Thank you. {{sticker:katarina-love}}
